name: "Transformers:The Movie" by Tom Whalen Scratch and Dent
description:
Sometimes things just happened, and unfortunately it happened with this print. This is a “Transformers: the Movie” by Tom Whalen. 24″ x 36″ 7-color Screenprint Timed edition number 10 that has seen better times. If you're a collector, you'll understand anything that any damage is a bad thing and that's what happened here.

The top left corner was bent in storage, so we can't see putting this is someone else's collection, so we were going to staple it to the wall.

Better heads prevailed and we thought someone should own this beautiful print even it's a little "tweaked," so if you want a Whalen at a discounted price, use this discount code: WHALENSHURT.

There's only one print so have it.
